title: Doom 1 & 2 MACOSX (wineskin)
description:
BADSADDAM STUDIOS WineSKIN

Doom 1 & 2 for mac osx wineskin!

this is the actual windows 95 doom 1 & 2 game and this is not a port version or any other crap this is the classic win95 version.

the only thing that sucks is the screen resolution is 640x480 but still very good to play.
